trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell" /> objects that are the cells of an <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell" /> que são as células de um controle <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow.HtmlTableCellControlCollection> class represents a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell> objects for an <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow> control.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow.HtmlTableCellControlCollection> classe representa uma coleção de <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell> objetos para um <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow> controle.

trans-unit.source: Controls can be added at the end of a collection with the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow.HtmlTableCellControlCollection.Add%2A> method or at a specified index location in the collection with the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow.HtmlTableCellControlCollection.AddAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Controles podem ser adicionados ao final de uma coleção com o <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow.HtmlTableCellControlCollection.Add%2A> método ou em um local de índice especificado na coleção com o <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow.HtmlTableCellControlCollection.AddAt%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: Only controls of type <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell> can be added to the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow.HtmlTableCellControlCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Somente controles do tipo <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell> podem ser adicionados para o <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableRow.HtmlTableCellControlCollection> coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> a adicionar à coleção.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> object to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> especificado à coleção.

trans-unit.source: The added control can only be an <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell> control; otherwise, an <xref:System.ArgumentException> exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: O controle adicionado só pode ser um <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell> controle; caso contrário, um <xref:System.ArgumentException> exceção será lançada.

trans-unit.source: The added control must be of type <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell" />.
trans-unit.target: O controle adicionado deve ser do tipo <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell" />.

trans-unit.source: The location in the array at which to add the child control.
trans-unit.target: O local na matriz à qual você deseja adicionar o controle filho.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> a adicionar à coleção.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> object to the collection at the specified index location.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Control" /> especificado à coleção no local de índice especificado.

trans-unit.source: The added control can only be an <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell> control; otherwise, an <xref:System.ArgumentException> exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: O controle adicionado só pode ser um <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell> controle; caso contrário, um <xref:System.ArgumentException> exceção será lançada.

trans-unit.source: The added control must be of type <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell" />.
trans-unit.target: O controle adicionado deve ser do tipo <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlTableCell" />.
